data.description: Have your own little slice of nature!  This rustic Log (vinyl) home is tucked away in total privacy on 4.21 acres.  Start each day with coffee on the front porch or back deck with just you, the sounds of the breeze flowing through nature and the surrounding wildlife.  Plenty of gardening space, and the seasonal wet weather branch just adds another element of relaxation!  Inside, you'll find very spacious living spaces great for entertaining and everything you'd expect in a modern home. High ceilings, beautiful trim work,  open spaces, split bedroom with 2 primary suites that is perfect for visitors. Main primary bath with walk-in tile shower and jetted tub.  Call to see it today!  *All information to be verified by purchaser*
